{"id":"202201278355","sourceId":"dow-jones","sourceName":"Global News Select","providerName":"Dow Jones","title":"Lowe's, Petco Plan Store-in-Store Concept","publishedDate":"2022-01-27T07:28:00-06:00","body":[{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n  By Matt Grossman ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"pre","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n  Lowe's Cos. and Petco Health and Wellness Company Inc. plan to open 15 store-in-store retail concepts inside Lowe's locations in three states, the companies said Thursday. ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n  The pair cited a rise in interest in pet ownership during the pandemic as the rationale behind the arrangement. The stores will sell pet food, supplies and services. ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n  The first location is set to open early next month in San Antonio. Other locations in Texas, North Carolina and South Carolina will follow in March. ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"pre","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n  Write to Matt Grossman at matt.grossman@wsj.com ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"pre","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n  (END) Dow Jones Newswires","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n  January 27, 2022 08:28 ET (13:28 GMT)","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n\nCopyright (c) 2022 Dow Jones & Company, Inc.","gated":false}]}